    <item>
      <title>康涅狄格州共和党议员反对未来禁止使用燃气汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/25/nx-s1-4996585-e1/republican-lawmakers-in-connecticut-fight-a-future-ban-on-gas-powered-vehicles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在民主党占多数的康涅狄格州立法机构中，一小部分共和党人设法使该州放弃了逐步淘汰燃气汽车销售的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/25/nx-s1-4996585-e1/republican-lawmakers-in-connecticut-fight-a-future-ban-on-gas-powered-vehicles</guid>
