    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通货膨胀导致慈善团体的支出增加，同时捐款减少</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/25/nx-s1-5017877/inflation-has-driven-expenses-up-for-charity-groups-while-driving-donations-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[慈善捐赠在 2022 年下降之后，去年有所回升。但通货膨胀正在蚕食捐赠的价值，给捐赠者和非营利组织都带来了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/25/nx-s1-5017877/inflation-has-driven-expenses-up-for-charity-groups-while-driving-donations-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 22:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
